;; Declarative catalogue for review and compatibility checks. Nix service arguments,
;; not this file, select the executing provider/model/effort. `codex-login` means
;; the Codex executable's already-authenticated ambient session; it does not select
;; or resolve an account, and never carries session material or credential values.
(ProviderPolicy openai-codex (AmbientSessionReference codex-login) (Production gpt-5.6-terra Medium) (CompatibilityTest gpt-5.6-luna Medium) [api-key token secret endpoint-credential])
